 |   C                     Z-ADDTIMESS    BAKOSS
 |   C                     MOVEL#USER     BAKOME
 |   C                     MOVEL#PGM      BANOPG
 |   C                     Z-ADD@2TNK     BATANK
 |   C                     UPDATAB#PLA81
 |   C                     ENDIF
JW1  C                     ENDDO
