E-01 ENTER CUSTOMER CODE
E-02 NO DATA IN DETAIL M/F
E-03 ENTER DELIVERY CODE
E-04 NO DATA IN DETAIL M/F
E-05 NO DATA IN SHIPMENT M/F
E-06 ENTER USER PARTS NO.
E-07 ENTER REVISED UNIT PRICE
E-08 ENTER EFFECTIVE DATE
E-09 EFFECTIVE DATE IS INVALID
E-10 ENTER EXP DATE
E-11 EXP DATE IS INVALID
E-12 EFFECTIVE DATE IS GREATER THAN EXP DATE
E-13 NEW EFFECTIVE DATE SHOULD BE GRATER THAN CURRENT EFFECTIVE
E-14 DELIVERY CODE IS DUPLICATE
E-15 UNIT PRICE SHOULD NOT BE MORE THAN $50 !
